			<h3 ><a href="#p113505">Re: Will 2 lighthouses work for what I need? (Diagram includ</a></h3>
			<p class="author"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=113505&amp;sid=cc8feaff7adf767811dcf78d6ff6e4f1#p113505"><img src="./styles/robotreviews/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="11" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a>by <strong><a href="./memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=21151&amp;sid=cc8feaff7adf767811dcf78d6ff6e4f1">carwashguy</a></strong> &raquo; January 25th, 2013, 6:09 pm </p>

			

